Invocation Name: ten minute books
des:
🧠BECOME SMARTER & LEARN FASTER 
10 minute books give you the key insights from bestseller books in 10 minutes or less: 
•In-App Recommendations. 
•Hundreds actionable insights and tips from the world’s greatest minds. 
•Readings by a diverse group of voice actors. 
•New books added each week!

Popular Categories: 
•Motivational Books 
•Psychology 
•History 
•Biographies 
•Finance 

Popular titles: 
•7 Habits of Highly Effective People 
•The Alchemist 
•Rich Dad Poor Dad 
•Sapiens, A Brief History of Humankind 
•Steve Jobs 
•The Five Love Languages 
•Grit, The Power Of Passion and Perseverance 
•The Autobiography of Malcolm X 
•The Art Of Happiness 
•Thinking, Fast and Slow 
•The Total Money Makeover 

Are we missing a book you’d like to get the key insights for? Let us know in the review section and we'll work on it!
